\Ax{\endowxn}=v\qx{x}+v\px{x}\cdot\Ax{\endow{x+1}{n-1}}=\Ax{\term{x}{t}}+\Ax{\pureendow{x}{t}}\cdot\Ax{\endow{x+t}{n-t}}
$
