\Ax{\pureendowxn}=v\px{x}\cdot\Ax{\pureendow{x+1}{n-1}}=\Ax{\term{x}{t}}+\Ax{\pureendow{x}{t}}\cdot\Ax{\pureendow{x+t}{n-t}}
